{"tid":1768330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳茂波：期望香港能在和平及充滿希望中前進","createTime":"2019-12-04T03:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T03:58:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dce69c7d132abb7f77590cda2436666ee6e74b29","tid":1768330,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:50:45.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波出席一項活動時表示，現時沒有任何事比修復社會撕裂更重要，政府已經致力進行持續的對話和積極溝通，期望香港能在和平和充滿希望的環境中前進。<br />\n<br />\n他在一個有關電子商貿的論壇上致辭時又提到，金管局推出的快速支付系統(FPS)，已經錄得超過360萬個登記，每日交易量超過15萬宗，涉及金額超過22億元。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波指，政府已經接受以FPS交稅及其他費用，現時正建立一個普及的二維碼標準，期望幫助推廣手機零售支付，改善商戶及消費者體驗，現時正努力建立智慧城市，相信有關政策將有助為中小企業及初創企業提供發展機會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1495888_1_L_20191204111958.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1495888_1_L_20191204111958.jpg&h=cea69851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495888-20191204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495888-20191204.htm&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=27834597\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495888-20191204.htm&h=03f533c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495888-20191204.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a5cf503be9ae67e8fae8e13d35ade518aab97b06","tid":1768330,"uid":172349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"我也期望陳荗波露宿街頭"},{"pid":"65ed243f41dc19f5a5668b6a087be50b6d9e5fd6","tid":1768330,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:55:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"3a216b6e61335a56a33c3495255610ad4c63860a","tid":1768330,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"劏房波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}